The paper focuses on image super-resolution using deep convolutional neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a new attention mechanism and a new block architecture, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural networks (cs.NE).
